{"lemma":"حِيالَ","slug":"حِيالَ","root":"حل","root_slug":"حل","root_link":"/words/roots/حل","pos":"PREP","pos_camel":"prep","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","prep"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n9600","n9789","n9791"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of حَائِل (ḥāʔil)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"masculine plural of حَائِل (ḥāʔil)","tags":["form-of","masculine","plural"]},{"pos":"prep","gloss":"opposite, forenenst"},{"pos":"prep","gloss":"in view of, in respect to, in regard of","examples":[{"text":".وشددت الحكومة المؤقتة في قرارها (…) على الإدارات المختصة اتخاذ مايلزم حياله من إجراء.","english":"The provisional government, in its decision, emphasized in address to the competent authorities to take the measure which is necessary in regard of it."},{"text":".أعلن وزير الخارجية السعودي عادل الجبير، الثلاثاء، أن بلاده تؤيد موقف الرئيس الأميركي دونالد ترمب حيال إيران","english":"The Saudi Minister of the Exterior ʿādil al-Gubayr announced on Tuesday that his country supports the position of the American President Donald Trump in regard of Iran."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"barrenness (of a she-camel)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n9600","headword_ar":"حِيَالٌ","root":"Hwl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HayAl","text_ar":"حَيال"},{"kind":"text","text":"] The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"front"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing, as meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part, place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"location, that is over against, opposite, facing, fronting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in front;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qubaAlapN","text_ar":"قُبَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, and Mgh in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hyl","text_ar":"حيل"},{"kind":"text","text":".) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qumotu HiyaAlahu","text_ar":"قُمْتُ حِيَالَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I stood in front of him; in the part, place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"location, that was over against him, opposite to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qubaAlatahu","text_ar":"قُبَالَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hyl","text_ar":"حيل"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEada HiyaAlapN","text_ar":"قَعَدَ حِيَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"page_break","n":677},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biHiyaAlihi","text_ar":"بِحِيَالِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sat in front of him, over against him, opposite to him, facing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fronting him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA_izaAy^ihi","text_ar":"بِاـِزَايِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA HiyaAla kalimatika","text_ar":"هٰذَا حِيَالَ كَلِمَتِكَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is opposite to thy saying;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muqaAbalapa","text_ar":"مُقَابَلَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; in the accus. case, as an adv. n. of place: thus related by IAar from the Arabs: but one may also say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiyaAlu kalimatika","text_ar":"حِيَالُ كَلِمَتِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the opposite of thy saying"},{"kind":"text","text":"], making the phrase to consist of an inchoative and an enunciative: so says ISd. (TA.) It is originally with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the place of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY HiyaAlihi","text_ar":"عَلَى حِيَالِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"By himself"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"itself; independently"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoTi kul~a waAHidK minohumo EalaY","text_ar":"اَعْطِ كُلَّ وَاحِدٍ مِنْهُمْ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiyaAlahu","text_ar":"حِيَالَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Give thou to every one of them by himself;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ElY Hidatihi","text_ar":"على حِدَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wHd","text_ar":"وحد"},{"kind":"text","text":";) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA@nofiraAdihi","text_ar":"بِا@نْفِرَادِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hyl","text_ar":"حيل"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalotu kul~a $aYo'K EalaY","text_ar":"فَعَلْتُ كُلَّ شَىْءٍ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiyaAlihi","text_ar":"حِيَالِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I did everything by itself;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA@nofiraAdihi","text_ar":"بِا@نْفِرَادِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hyl","text_ar":"حيل"},{"kind":"text","text":".)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A string that is tied from the camel's"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biTaAn","text_ar":"بِطَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"belly-girth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haqab","text_ar":"حَقَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hind girth"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to prevent the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haqab","text_ar":"حَقَب"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from going against the sheath of his penis:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) so, too, in the M: but in the O, as on the authority of AA, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuwalN","text_ar":"حُوَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuradN","text_ar":"صُرَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"string that is between the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haqab","text_ar":"حَقَب"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biTaAn","text_ar":"بِطَان"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K"]},{"entry_id":"n9789","headword_ar":"حِيَالٌ","root":"Hyl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiyaAlahu","text_ar":"حِيَالَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biHiyaAlihi","text_ar":"بِحِيَالِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY HiyaAlihi","text_ar":"عَلَى حِيَالِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hwl","text_ar":"حول"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n9791","headword_ar":"حَيَّالٌ","root":"Hyl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see its syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huw~alN","text_ar":"حُوَّلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hwl","text_ar":"حول"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}